# Articles

All the files inside `/_pages` are licensed under
[CC BY 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/). The attribution requirement is only met when:

1. The canonical link is directed towards the original article, e.g.
   `<link rel="canonical" href="{the actual blog article link on this website}" />`
2. The following message is displayed above and below the article:
   `This article has been originally published on <a href="{this blog's link}">Praful's Blog</a>.`

